{"word":"G496 - ἀντιπίπτω - antipíptō - an-tee-pip'-to - Resist","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντιπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antipíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-tee-pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Resist</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எதிர்த்து நில்"},{"paragraph":"to fall upon, run against, to be adverse, oppose, strive against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a> (including its alternate); to <i>oppose:</i> - resist.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}